keyMappings:
unmap <c-e>
unmap <c-y>
unmap p
unmap P
unmap t

map ~ visitPreviousTab
map D scrollPageUp
map gd LinkHints.activateModeToDownloadLink
map gh createTab
map gJ scrollFullPageDown
map gK scrollFullPageUp
map go LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map H previousTab
map J goForward
map K goBack
map L nextTab
map P LinkHints.activateModeToOpenIncognito
map pp openCopiedUrlInCurrentTab
map pP openCopiedUrlInNewTab
map qH closeTabsOnLeft
map qL closeTabsOnRight
map qo closeOtherTabs
map qq removeTab
map t Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map u restoreTab
